# ğŸ§® 75. Sort Colors

ğŸ”— https://leetcode.com/problems/sort-colors/description/

## âœ… Approach:
uses 3 variables or pointers
2 to track and add first and last element(0,2)
mid pointer to traverse
if 0 and 2 placed 1s will be automatically placed in the right place
## â±ï¸ Time Complexity:
- O(n) time, O(1) space

## ğŸ”¤ Code (Java):
```java
class Solution {
    public void sortColors(int[] nums) {
        int low=0;
        int mid=0;
        int high=nums.length-1;
        while(mid<=high){
            if(nums[mid]==0){
                int temp=nums[low];
                nums[low]=nums[mid];
                nums[mid]=temp;
                low++;
                mid++;
            }
            else if(nums[mid]==1){
                mid++;
            }
            else{
                int temp=nums[high];
                nums[high]=nums[mid];
                nums[mid]=temp;
                high--;
            }
        }
        return;
    }
}
